{"tid":1224272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不撤回 不收貨 不接受暫緩 616星期日遊行見！","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T03:04:43.000Z","uid":124584,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9329c86cfd97a405e1340413b3625e465afe7fe1","tid":1224272,"uid":124584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"林奠，我地香港人聽日收你皮！"},{"pid":"ee08e6aa6b4597b93cc56363111fb67ec28dc2a7","tid":1224272,"uid":168840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"16919fc329bf6e44eda19e2d5b0649255bab2780","tid":1224272,"uid":124584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b7037c863ddbf59dde3ab10e1518493b48edbf87","tid":1224272,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:19.000Z","msg":"[緊急/請廣傳] 政府暫緩以退為進，星期日香港人唔出嚟將會一敗塗地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224213\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224213</a><br />\n<br />\n經過69百萬人遊行同612血腥鎮壓，政府既管治合法性已經危在旦夕，全世界都等緊機會作致命一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家政府扮聽民意暫緩修例，目的係以退為進，買時間令善忘既香港人沖淡怒氣，同時令國際社會無機會出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果香港人因為政府暫緩而星期日唔出嚟，之後將會係連場既大規模清算同白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時候無人會再敢抗爭，惡法原封不動通過，69既百萬人遊行，612義士既犧牲將會毀於一旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你唔想呢件事發生，就要趁全世界站係香港人一方，民氣最強既時候出黎遊行，堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場仗冇階段性勝利，一係贏，一係輸，winner takes all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港要贏，香港人星期日一定要出嚟，多你一個絕對好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊記目標只有一個：撤回惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家copy呢個post喺Facebook, IG, Whatsapp share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣組幫手整圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用盡你一切方法動員認識既人星期日出嚟堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3c3d638bbdd9d0e18fb11c161aed802b8a2a09","tid":1224272,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChPmgyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChPmgyt.png&h=a1111301&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"513a23b91ef146ff7d87d73b4788d8f645af7966","tid":1224272,"uid":111578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:53:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散</span></span>"},{"pid":"0950b807e44fe3fa673668667e45f92edc6b3941","tid":1224272,"uid":124584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 仲有班比警犬拘捕左既戰友 一定要無條件釋放</span></span>"},{"pid":"6773b4d7399dd6c945f9c782d3f33bf6bb0391e5","tid":1224272,"uid":111578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散</span></span>"}]}